<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <title>Login</title>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="~/Content/Assets/Login/images/icons/favicon.ico" />
    <link rel="stylesheet"
          type="text/css"
          href="~/Content/Assets/Login/vendor/bootstrap/css/bootstrap.min.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet"
          type="text/css"
          href="~/Content/Assets/Login/fonts/font-awesome-4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet"
          type="text/css"
          href="~/Content/Assets/Login/fonts/iconic/css/material-design-iconic-font.min.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet"
          type="text/css"
          href="~/Content/Assets/Login/vendor/animate/animate.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet"
          type="text/css"

          href="~/Content/Assets/Login/vendor/css-hamburgers/hamburgers.min.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet"
          type="text/css"
          href="~/Content/Assets/Login/vendor/animsition/css/animsition.min.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet"
          type="text/css"
          href="~/Content/Assets/Login/vendor/select2/select2.min.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet"
          type="text/css"
          href="~/Content/Assets/Login/vendor/daterangepicker/daterangepicker.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="~/Content/Assets/Login/css/util.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="~/Content/Assets/Login/css/main.css" />
    <style>
        .text-center1 {
            color: black;
            font-size: 22px;
        }

        body, html {
            height: 100%;
            margin: 0;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
            background-color: #ffffff; /* ✅ Đổi từ xám sang trắng */
        }

        .login-wrapper {
            height: 100vh;
            background-color: #ffffff; /* ✅ Đảm bảo wrapper cũng trắng */
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .login-row {
            height: 100%;
        }

        .left-panel {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #007f5f, #2b9348);
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            border-bottom-left-radius: 250px 100px;
            border-top-right-radius: 200px 300px; /* cần giữ */
            z-index: 1;
            overflow: hidden;
            padding-bottom: 80px;
        }

        .right-panel {
            background: #ffffff;
            border-top-right-radius: 200px 300px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .left-panel, .right-panel {
            transition: border-radius 0.3s ease;
        }



        .login-form-container {
            background: white;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: none;
            width: 100%;
        }
        /*
                    input[type="text"], input[type="password"] {
                        margin-bottom: 15px;
                        border-radius: 10px;
                        border: 1px solid #ccc;
                        padding: 10px;
                    }
                 */
        .btn-outline-light {
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 10px 25px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out;
        }

            .btn-outline-light:hover {
                background-color: white;
                color: #007f5f;
                transform: scale(1.05);
            }

        .left-panel > * {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .bg-green-overlay {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            right: 0;
            width: 50%;
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #007f5f, #2b9348);
            z-index: 0;
        }

    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container-fluid login-wrapper position-relative">
        <div class="bg-green-overlay"></div>
        <div class="row login-row position-relative">
            <div class="col-md-6 left-panel d-flex flex-column justify-content-center align-items-center text-white px-4">
                <h2 style="font-size: 40; padding:90px">Chào mừng bạn trở lại!</h2>
                <p class="text-center1 px-5">
                    Đây là hệ thống quản lý yêu cầu sự cố dành cho doanh nghiệp.
                    <br />
                    Vui lòng đăng nhập để tiếp tục theo dõi, xử lý và cập nhật trạng thái các yêu cầu từ các công ty một cách hiệu quả và nhanh chóng.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="col-md-6 right-panel d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center">
                <div class="login-form-container w-75">
                    @RenderBody()
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    @RenderSection("Modals", required: false)
</body>

</html>

